==English==

===Etymology===
Possibly from Latin ''[[timorosus]]'', from Latin ''[[timor]]'', '''fear''', + adjective suffix ''[[-ous]]'', from Latin suffix ''[[-osus]]'' with general meaning of '''full of'''

===Adjective===
'''timorous'''

